{"article_id":"WJX6EIfNAb2hmmSD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump signed an executive order Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"paving the way for an overhaul of the way","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"kidney disease ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"which affects 30 million Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"is treated in the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The president 's move would lead to sweeping changes in treatment as well as prevention ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"including improving access to dialysis treatment in the home and enabling people with failing kidneys to have opportunities sooner","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to get a transplant .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` This is a first , second and third step ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"it ' s more than just a first step , \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"said Trump","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"just before signing the executive order .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"\" We ' re going to come up with solutions over a period of five years and 10 years ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"most people won ' t believe . \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"And","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"because a severe organ shortage complicates the call for more transplants ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"the administration also aims to ease financial hardships for living donors ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"said the officials ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"who spoke on the condition of anonymity ahead of the announcement .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"STEVIE WONDER SAYS","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"HE 'LL UNDERGO KIDNEY TRANSPLANT LATER THIS YEAR","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"Another key change :","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"steps","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to help the groups","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that collect deceased donations","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"do a better job .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Officials cited a study","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that suggests","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"long term it may be possible to find 17,000 more kidneys and 11,000 other organs from deceased donors for transplant every year .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Federal health officials have made clear for months","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"that they intend to shake up a system","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that today favors expensive , time-consuming dialysis in large centers over easier-to-tolerate at-home care or transplants","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that help patients live longer .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" For 50 years , we have had basically a stagnant system","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"of how we treat people with chronic kidney disease , \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Health and Human Services Secretary Alex M. Azar II said in a briefing","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"held Wednesday morning .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" Right now every financial incentive is toward dialysis","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and not toward transplantation and long-term survivorship , \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Azar ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"whose father experienced traditional and at-home dialysis","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"before getting a living donor transplant ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"told a Senate hearing in March .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" And you get what you pay for . \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"About 30 million American adults have chronic kidney disease ,","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"costing Medicare a staggering $ 113 billion .","depth":3},{"id":48,"text":"Careful treatment","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"- including control of diabetes and high blood pressure , the two main culprits -","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"can help prevent further kidney deterioration .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"But more than 700,000 people have end-stage renal disease ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"meaning their kidneys have failed ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and require either a transplant or dialysis","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"to survive .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Only about a third received specialized kidney care","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"before they got so sick .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"More than 94,000 of the 113,000 people on the national organ waiting list need a kidney .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Last year , there were 21,167 kidney transplants .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"A fraction","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"- 6,442 -","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"were from living donors ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"according to the United Network for Organ Sharing ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"which oversees the nation ' s transplant system .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"\" The longer you ' re on dialysis ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"the outcomes are worse , \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"said Dr. Amit Tevar , a transplant surgeon at the University of Pittsburgh Medical Center ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"who praised the Trump administration initiatives","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"being announced Wednesday .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Too often , transplant centers don ' t see a kidney patient","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"until they ' ve been on dialysis for years ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"while any transplant is preferable ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"one from a living donor is best","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"because those organs \" work better , longer and faster , \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Tevar said .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"-Medicare payment changes","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that would provide a financial incentive for doctors and clinics","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to help kidney patients stave off end-stage disease by about six months .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"-A bonus to kidney specialists","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who help prepare patients for early transplant , with steps","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that can begin","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"even before they need dialysis .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"-Additional Medicare changes","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"so that dialysis providers can earn as much","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"by helping patients get dialysis at home as in the large centers","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that predominate today .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Patients typically must spend hours three or four times a week","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"hooked to machines","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"that filter waste out of their blood .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Home options include portable blood-cleansing machines , or what ' s called peritoneal dialysis","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that works through an abdominal tube ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"usually while patients are sleeping .","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"Today , about 14 % of patients in kidney failure get at-home dialysis or an early transplant .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"By 2025 , the goal is to have 80 % of people with newly diagnosed kidney failure","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"getting one of those options ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"officials said .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"These changes are being implemented through Medicare ' s innovation center ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"created under the Obama-era Affordable Care Act","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"and empowered","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"to seek savings and improved quality .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"The Trump administration is relying on the innovation center","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"even as it argues in federal court","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that the law","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"that created it","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"is unconstitutional","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"and should be struck down entirely .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Other initiatives will require new regulations ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"expected to be proposed later this year .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Among them :","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"-Allowing reimbursement of lost wages and other expenses for living donors ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"who can give one of their kidneys or a piece of their liver .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"The transplant recipient ' s insurance pays the donor ' s medical bills .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"But they are out of work for weeks recuperating","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and one study found","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"more than a third of living kidney donors reported lost wages , a median of $ 2,712 , in the year","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"following donation .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Details","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"about who pays","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"- and who qualifies -","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"still have to be worked out .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"-Clearer ways","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to measure how well the nation ' s 58 organ procurement organizations collect donations from deceased donors .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Some do a better job than others ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"but today ' s performance standards are self-reported ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"varying around the country","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"and making it hard for government regulators or the OPOs themselves to take steps","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"to improve . \"","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Some OPOs are very aggressive","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"and move forward with getting organs allocated and donors consented ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and there are those","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"that are a little more lackadaisical about it , \"","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"said Pittsburgh ' s Tevar .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Unlike the medical advances in transplantation , \" we haven ' t really made big dents and progress and moves","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"in increasing cadaveric organs or increasing live donor options . \"","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"This story is based on reporting by The Associated Press .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":182,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":157,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":152,"right":156,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":141,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":0,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":139,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":1,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":143,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":5,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":12,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":154,"right":155,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":16,"right":153,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":158,"right":180,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity"